Monique Armistead-Pitchford, Assistant Principal of Special Education at Oswego CUSD 308, says EmbraceIEP® software helps her team progress monitor and keep up with dates more effectively.

Another Embrace® feature Oswego CUSD 308 staff loves is Goal Builder.

“The goal builder is really helpful. To be able to go in and build goals that are specific to our students, while also implementing the data that we need for their actual goals as they move through the school year.”
